text: Jeng Shwu-zen (born 2 June 1977) is a Taiwanese badminton player. She competed in women's singles at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Taiwan Category:Badminton players at the 1996 Summer Olympics
